author: Rhenanus, Johann, active 1610
title: Solis e puteo emergentis: sive dissertationis chymiotechnicae libri tres. In quibus totius operationis chymicae methodus practica: materia lapidis philosophici, et nodus [sic] solvendi ejus, operandique, ut et clavis operum Paracelsi qua abstrusa explican
